003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222022-08-02T18:57:01Z\u0022 title=\u002208/02/2022 06:57  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00221 yr\u0022\u003EAugust 2, 2022\u003C/time\u003E by kerbiloid\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"StrandedonEarth","CreatedById":89439,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-08-02T22:57:35Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224160483\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u002291282\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221659466613\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022129408\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022kerbiloid\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n3 hours ago, kerbiloid said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt entered this world in its time, but the greedy humans rejected it.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u0022How much???\u0022 asked they, trying to believe their ears.\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u0022Too expensive!!!\u0022 exlaimed they after the first shock.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBut if it\u2019s produced on an automated production line for long enough, the price per unit will drop like a rock\u2026.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe trick is finding enough suckers at $1600 per to pay for the production line\u2026\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Silavite","CreatedById":156204,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-08-07T04:39:49Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIs it just me, or does the vertical stabilizer on Boom\u0027s redesign look really undersized?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler\u0022 data-ipsspoiler=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_header\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003ESpoiler\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsEmbeddedVideo\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 height=\u0022113\u0022 src=\u0022https://www.youtube-nocookie.com/embed/eYxpWDpwsuY?feature=oembed\u0022 title=\u0022Meet Overture\u2019s refined design\u0022 width=\u0022200\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022overture-reveal-fuselage.jpg\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002266.67\u0022 height=\u0022800\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022https://boomsupersonic.com/static/images/overture-reveal-fuselage.jpg\u0022\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027m wondering how lateral stability (particularly C\u003Csub\u003EN\u003C/sub\u003E\u003Csub\u003E,\u03B2\u003C/sub\u003E) is achieved...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Shpaget","CreatedById":45577,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-08-07T09:11:39Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIntuitively, yes, they do look a bit small.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThey say \u002265\u002B\u0022 passengers. I count 33 windows, so two seats per row? I\u0027ve been inside Concorde, and that thing is tiny and cramped inside. This can\u0027t be much larger, can it?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNet zero carbon? What, the food \u003Cs\u003Ecart\u003C/s\u003E tray?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Superluminal Gremlin","CreatedById":221533,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-08-11T08:18:09Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIs having no excuse an excuse? Logically?\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"kerbiloid","CreatedById":129408,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-08-11T11:48:27Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt\u0027s a former cuse, an ex-cuse.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAlso, no accuse - no excuse. So, it\u0027s a problem of those who are accusing to get an excuse.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"SunlitZelkova","CreatedById":206402,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-08-11T23:18:28Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224162793\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u002291282\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221660205889\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022221533\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022TKMK\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n14 hours ago, TKMK said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIs having no excuse an excuse? Logically?\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDid you actually have no excuse?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIf you did not actually have any excuse it isn\u2019t an excuse from a physical point of view. The thing just happened.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBut humans have this thing called duty in their behavior so even if you had absolutely no way of doing whatever thing (and thus no excuse for whatever happened) you are expected to bear responsibility, and therefore having no excuse is an excuse.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBecause it is your fault regardless of the physical situation.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}